{"tid":2267572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對細眼嘅女仔就會忍唔住望","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:33:46.000Z","uid":307910,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d9fff97752b5ddc78eaf573572e06e7ef89d8a73","tid":2267572,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"以前唔洗帶口罩，五官基本上都可以睇到晒，時唔時正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家全部人帶晒口罩，眼佔成塊面嘅比例就好大，一見到一啲細眼嘅女仔就忍唔住望，覺得細眼嘅女仔好似成日迴避緊你嘅眼神，怕怕醜醜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾人發現你望佢我就望得更加勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱食晏見到有個戴口罩嘅囡囡，佢迎面行過嚟，我忍唔住係咁望佢，望到佢開心怕醜到跑走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知佢有冇上連登架呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50789755a0fb99570da491141db3550188a708f1","tid":2267572,"uid":77803,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"北佬啲劣質DNA都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513a3b0c4550503059ce359084b5d62396cd6400","tid":2267572,"uid":305631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"樓豬遲早成為強姦犯"},{"pid":"8a3cbed05606bf331d78843a97bb2046722657fd","tid":2267572,"uid":307910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50789755a0fb99570da491141db3550188a708f1","tid":2267572,"uid":77803,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"北佬啲劣質DNA都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT